<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Regensburg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Auskunft über König Sigismund von Ungarn und bittet um weitere Neuigkeiten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_278" id="138v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_278_r1l1"><expan>Reg<ex>enſpurg</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_278_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> . <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> . Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> deʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l3">künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l4">mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe / . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / Ob Jr fürbas dhein <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>ſchaft</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l5">davon erfürt / daʒ Jr vns das <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>verſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Erfüren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l6">wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ıcht das <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> davon ıcht eigenſchaft / das <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l7">wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> ſo <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l8">wir cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit auch nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jr vns ſchreıbt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l9">vnd das vil red ıſt lantmanſweıſe/ daʒ etlıche <expan>ſage<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l10">mainen / daʒ er <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſülle / So mainen etlıch nicht / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l12">daʒ wir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_278_r1l11">des </ab></add> noch kein <expan>aige<ex>n</ex>ſchaft</expan> wıſſen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l13">vıtȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_278" id="138v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Reg<ex>enspurg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dez künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleizze. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob ir fürbas dhein
                                <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>schaft</expan> davon erfürt, daz ir uns das
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet; erfüren wir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> davon icht eigenschaft, das
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                            <expan>Besund<ex>er</ex></expan> so <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        czü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit auch nicht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> als ir uns
                        schreibt und das vil red ist lantmansweise, daz etliche
                                <expan>sage<ex>n</ex></expan> und mainen, daz er
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sülle, so mainen etlich nicht, also
                        daz wir <add>des</add> noch kein <expan>aige<ex>n</ex>schaft</expan> wissen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti.</ab>
</div>
